trans-unit.source: The following information will describe the experience of using multi-factor authentication with your mobile or office phone.
trans-unit.target: The following information will describe the experience of using multi-factor authentication with your mobile or office phone.

trans-unit.source: To sign in with a call to your office or mobile phone
trans-unit.target: To sign in with a call to your office or mobile phone

trans-unit.source: Sign in to an application or service such as Office 365 using your user name and password.
trans-unit.target: Sign in to an application or service such as Office 365 using your user name and password.

trans-unit.source: Answer the phone and hit the # key.
trans-unit.target: Answer the phone and hit the # key.

trans-unit.source: You should now be signed in.
